{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/blog/2023/7/9/snippet/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<blockquote>\n<p>코드리뷰를 받는데, 멘토님께서 React.FC타입을 사용하셨다.<br>\n이전 한 블로그 글에서 React.FC에 대한 부정적인 사례를 설명해서 궁금증에 질문을 올리려했다.<br>\n무턱대고 질문을 올리는 습관은 좋지 못하다. 그 전에 먼저 찾아보고 찾아본 결과를 토대로 질문을 올렸다.<br>\n질문 올리기 전, 해당 내용에 대한 정리를 해보았다. TIL에 정리해놓은 내용을 다시 다듬어 블로그에 포스팅해본다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>먼저 왜 React.FC타입을 사용하지 않는 건지 찾아보았다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"reactfc-children\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reactfc-children\" aria-label=\"reactfc children permalink\" class=\"headerElement before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>React.FC children</h2>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a2f4bcba273470cdc4d1b1df610078f5/c7953/React.FC-chilren-default.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 17.1875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAkElEQVQI123HSwrCMBgA4Z5EF32/TfInaWJjiuD9jzQuhILi4mOYYg0ZSU+mmKl1oFLbX7XaaPSnlfLn/ypue6CTxCSRSQKzjyxbZLSeyTpG8Qzi6LWjXoVee0YX6bSnXIVyMZSLnIpG7rQm0ivPoBwmZfSeMPsDSQ9sPlAxMUjAHC90OhhtoF2Fa79w6eYvb6JPXm/tIlwlAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/a2f4bcba273470cdc4d1b1df610078f5/a59e9/React.FC-chilren-default.webp 192w,\n/static/a2f4bcba273470cdc4d1b1df610078f5/0ca9f/React.FC-chilren-default.webp 384w,\n/static/a2f4bcba273470cdc4d1b1df610078f5/dc9b9/React.FC-chilren-default.webp 768w,\n/static/a2f4bcba273470cdc4d1b1df610078f5/e2c2f/React.FC-chilren-default.webp 1152w,\n/static/a2f4bcba273470cdc4d1b1df610078f5/f3efb/React.FC-chilren-default.webp 1536w,\n/static/a2f4bcba273470cdc4d1b1df610078f5/691ec/React.FC-chilren-default.webp 1896w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/a2f4bcba273470cdc4d1b1df610078f5/3b721/React.FC-chilren-default.png 192w,\n/static/a2f4bcba273470cdc4d1b1df610078f5/66595/React.FC-chilren-default.png 384w,\n/static/a2f4bcba273470cdc4d1b1df610078f5/fe486/React.FC-chilren-default.png 768w,\n/static/a2f4bcba273470cdc4d1b1df610078f5/d2d74/React.FC-chilren-default.png 1152w,\n/static/a2f4bcba273470cdc4d1b1df610078f5/e8464/React.FC-chilren-default.png 1536w,\n/static/a2f4bcba273470cdc4d1b1df610078f5/c7953/React.FC-chilren-default.png 1896w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/a2f4bcba273470cdc4d1b1df610078f5/fe486/React.FC-chilren-default.png\"\n            alt=\"React.FC type have note children\"\n            title=\"React.FC type have note children\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">React.FC type have note children</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>children이 옵셔널 형태로 들어가 있었는데, <strong>React 18 version이 되면서 수정</strong>되었다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Props</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  children<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ReactNode<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Greetings<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">FC</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Props<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>children<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Hello, </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이 컴포넌트는 자식 컴포넌트가 꼭 필요하다는 의도를 타입으로 정의했다. 하지만, 원래는 children이 암묵적 옵셔널 형태로 들어가있었다.</p>\n<br>\n<p>즉, 수정 전에는 children을 Props 타입으로 명확히 드러내지 않아도 children을 매개변수로 선언했을 때 에러가 나지 않았던 것이다.</p>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"기명함수에-적용하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EB%AA%85%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98%EC%97%90-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"기명함수에 적용하기 permalink\" class=\"headerElement before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>기명함수에 적용하기</h2>\n<br>\n<p>자바스크립트에는 함수를 정의하는 대표적인 4가지 방식이 존재한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 함수 선언문</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 함수 표현식</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">add</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 화살표 함수</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">add</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 생성자 함수</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> add <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'x'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'return x + y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 3</span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<p>위 코드는 js기준인데, ts기준으로 다시 작성해보자</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ts\"><pre class=\"language-ts\"><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 익명 함수를 변수에 할당하여 타이핑</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> add<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">FC</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>x<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> y<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 또는 화살표함수로 작성할 수 있다</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> add<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">FC</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>x<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> y<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 하지만 기명함수 선언문으로 작성할 수 없다</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>지극히 개인적인 의견인데, 나는 리액트를 처음 배울 때 <code class=\"language-text\">화살표</code>함수를 사용하는 방법부터 배웠다.<br>\n그래서 함수선언문 표현방식을 잘 사용하지 않는다.</p>\n<br>\n<p>최근엔 사용하려고 시도했던 것을 생각해보니, next.js app directory내에서 <a href=\"https://nextjs.org/docs/pages/building-your-application/routing/api-routes\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">공식문서</a>를 보고 사용하려고 했던게 기억난다. next.js에서 예시문은 함수선언문으로 작성되어있다.<br>\n그래서 함수선언문으로 타이핑한 후 타입을 적용할 때 React.FC 타입을 매기려고 했는데, 적용되지 않았다.<br>\n결국 화살표함수로 변경해주었다.</p>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"reactfc-defaultprops\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reactfc-defaultprops\" aria-label=\"reactfc defaultprops permalink\" class=\"headerElement before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>React.FC defaultProps</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">AddProps</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  x<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  y<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Add</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> AddProps<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>x <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nAdd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>defaultProps <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  x<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  y<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> Add<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/febc6be74a36054004ce2db344859687/6e199/default-props-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 37.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/febc6be74a36054004ce2db344859687/a59e9/default-props-1.webp 192w,\n/static/febc6be74a36054004ce2db344859687/0ca9f/default-props-1.webp 384w,\n/static/febc6be74a36054004ce2db344859687/dc9b9/default-props-1.webp 768w,\n/static/febc6be74a36054004ce2db344859687/e2c2f/default-props-1.webp 1152w,\n/static/febc6be74a36054004ce2db344859687/f3efb/default-props-1.webp 1536w,\n/static/febc6be74a36054004ce2db344859687/19b3e/default-props-1.webp 2282w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/febc6be74a36054004ce2db344859687/3b721/default-props-1.png 192w,\n/static/febc6be74a36054004ce2db344859687/66595/default-props-1.png 384w,\n/static/febc6be74a36054004ce2db344859687/fe486/default-props-1.png 768w,\n/static/febc6be74a36054004ce2db344859687/d2d74/default-props-1.png 1152w,\n/static/febc6be74a36054004ce2db344859687/e8464/default-props-1.png 1536w,\n/static/febc6be74a36054004ce2db344859687/6e199/default-props-1.png 2282w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/febc6be74a36054004ce2db344859687/fe486/default-props-1.png\"\n            alt=\"JSX.element 타입일 때\"\n            title=\"JSX.element 타입일 때\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">JSX.element 타입일 때</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2f8d7b1f98dd4716674f55552d4f7430/6e199/default-props-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34.895833333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/2f8d7b1f98dd4716674f55552d4f7430/a59e9/default-props-2.webp 192w,\n/static/2f8d7b1f98dd4716674f55552d4f7430/0ca9f/default-props-2.webp 384w,\n/static/2f8d7b1f98dd4716674f55552d4f7430/dc9b9/default-props-2.webp 768w,\n/static/2f8d7b1f98dd4716674f55552d4f7430/e2c2f/default-props-2.webp 1152w,\n/static/2f8d7b1f98dd4716674f55552d4f7430/f3efb/default-props-2.webp 1536w,\n/static/2f8d7b1f98dd4716674f55552d4f7430/19b3e/default-props-2.webp 2282w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/2f8d7b1f98dd4716674f55552d4f7430/3b721/default-props-2.png 192w,\n/static/2f8d7b1f98dd4716674f55552d4f7430/66595/default-props-2.png 384w,\n/static/2f8d7b1f98dd4716674f55552d4f7430/fe486/default-props-2.png 768w,\n/static/2f8d7b1f98dd4716674f55552d4f7430/d2d74/default-props-2.png 1152w,\n/static/2f8d7b1f98dd4716674f55552d4f7430/e8464/default-props-2.png 1536w,\n/static/2f8d7b1f98dd4716674f55552d4f7430/6e199/default-props-2.png 2282w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/2f8d7b1f98dd4716674f55552d4f7430/fe486/default-props-2.png\"\n            alt=\"React.FC 타입일 때\"\n            title=\"React.FC 타입일 때\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">React.FC 타입일 때</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>위 캡처본에서 볼 수 있듯이, React.FC 타입으로 default props를 지정해주면 에러가 난다.</p>\n<p>하지만, 과연 default props를 사용하는 경우가 많을까?<br>\ndefault props를 사용하는 경우는 오히려 가독성이 더 떨어지지 않을까?<br>\nprops로 내려주는 값을 상위 컴포넌트에서 확인할 수 없으니 말이다.</p>\n<p>최근 가독성 좋은 코드에 대해서 생각해봤을 때, 하위(자식)컴포넌트를 눌러보지 않고, 부모컴포넌트에서 어떤 props가 어떻게 내려가는지 알 수 있는 코드가 가독성 좋은 코드라는 생각이 들었다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">App</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">BlogPost</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">x</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">y</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>위 코드를 그대로 가져와서 사용했을 때 default props를 사용하면 BlogPost에 어떤 prop을 받는지 부모입장에선 알 수 없다.\n이 말은 즉, BlogPost를 열거나, 드래그 해봐야 알 수 있다.</p>\n<br>\n<hr>\n<p>적고나니 들었던 생각인데, 내가 불편하게 생각하는 요소는 존재하지 않는 듯하다.<br>\n현재 나의 프로젝트에서는 <code class=\"language-text\">React.FC타입</code>을 적극적으로 사용하고 있고, 지금까진 크게 문제되지 않았다.</p>\n<br>\n<p><a href=\"https://geuni620.github.io/blog/2023/5/20/%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90%EC%9D%98_%EC%BB%A4%EB%A6%AC%EC%96%B4/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">개발자 커리어에 정해진 방향이 없듯이</a> 개발의 세계에서도 정답이 존재하지 않는다.</p>\n<p>위에 적은 내용 역시 온전히 <strong>‘나의’</strong> 기준일 뿐, 다른 분들은 이렇게 생각하지 않을 수도 있다.<br>\n실제, 단톡방에서 React.FC타입보단, JSX.element가 자동추론되는 것이 더 나은 방법이라고 권하시는 분들도 계셨다.</p>\n<p>결국, 정답이 없으니, 맞춰가면 되는게 아닐까?<br>\n팀원과 소통하고, 충분한 의견 교환 이후 방향을 결정하면 되는 듯 하다.\n고집을 부릴 필요 없고, 팀원이 JSX.element를 쓰자고 하면, 그에 맞게 FC 타입을 권해본 뒤, 타협점을 찾을 것 같다.</p>\n<br>\n<p>최근에 소프트 스킬, 특히 커뮤니케이션이 갈 수록 중요해질 것이라는 이야기를 들었다.<br>\n완전 공감하는 요즘이다.</p>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"참고자료\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0%EC%9E%90%EB%A3%8C\" aria-label=\"참고자료 permalink\" class=\"headerElement before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고자료</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://react.vlpt.us/using-typescript/02-ts-react-basic.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. 리액트 컴포넌트 타입스크립트로 작성하기</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yceffort.kr/2022/03/dont-use-react-fc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">React.FC를 사용하지 않는 이유</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itchallenger.tistory.com/641\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">타입스크립트 : React.FC는 그만! children 타이핑 올바르게 하기</a></p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#reactfc-children\">React.FC children</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EB%AA%85%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98%EC%97%90-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">기명함수에 적용하기</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#reactfc-defaultprops\">React.FC defaultProps</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0%EC%9E%90%EB%A3%8C\">참고자료</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"React.FC가 그렇게 이상한가요?","summary":"-","date":"2023.07.22.","categories":["개발"]}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2023/7/9/snippet/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1629908903"]}